242
00:11:34,103 --> 00:11:36,063
is not a reflection on you as a person.

243
00:11:37,080 --> 00:11:40,501
A lot of the time, that unfinished animation is only imperfect to you.

244
00:11:40,761 --> 00:11:42,822
To everyone else, the animation is finished.

245
00:11:44,242 --> 00:11:47,944
And remember, you can always go back and polish your favorite animations for your demo reel

